file.name: swagger.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: auth-service
  version: version not set

paths:
  /api/v1/token:
    post:
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/x-www-form-urlencoded:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                grant_type:          # <!--- form field name
                  type: string
                username:    # <!--- form field name
                  type: string
                password:    # <!--- form field name
                  type: string
              required:
                - grant_type
                - username
                - password
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                 access_token:
                   type: string
                 expires_in:
                   type: number
                 refresh_token:
                   type: string
                 token_type:
                   type: string
          description: OK
        '400':
          description: Bad request.
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                 access_token:
                   type: string
